|---|-------|-------|----------|
| 1 | `/users` exposes PII without auth | A01 | **High** |
| 2 | No helmet / CORS / `x-powered-by` disabled | A05 | Medium |
| 3 | No rate limiting | A04 | Medium |
| 4 | HTTP only, hardcoded port, binds 0.0.0.0 | A02 | Medium |
| 5 | No error-handling middleware | A05/A09 | Low-Med |
| 6 | No request logging | A09 | Low |
| 7 | No input-validation scaffolding (future-proofing) | A03 | Low |
| 8 | No visible dependency-audit policy | A06 | Low |
| 9 | `app.listen` runs on `require()` | — | Low (quality) |

