app.get('/users', requireAuth, (req, res) => {
  const users = getUsers();
  // Only return emails if caller has permission
  const sanitized = users.map(u => ({
    id: u.id,
    name: u.name,
    ...(req.user.canViewEmails ? { email: u.email } : {}),
  }));
  res.json(sanitized);
});
```

### 2. Missing security headers (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)

No `helmet()` middleware; responses ship without `Strict-Transport-Security`, `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Content-Security-Policy`, etc.

